data.description: Looking for a spacious home for family and guests with a BOAT DOCK?  This custom home has a reverse floor plan with three bedrooms, bath, laundry room and large family room with French doors leading out to a large, covered, cement patio with views of the Manatee River and Skyway Bridge on first level.  Upstairs there are 12-foot ceilings throughout and vaulted ceilings in the living and dining area. The 49X10 foot covered front porch has access from the dining area through a wall of French doors.  For cool nights, lite the wood burning fireplace, enjoyed from all areas including the open kitchen, wet bar and den/library.   Leave the wet bar and enjoy a tranquil back screened porch, again with even better views of the water and Bridge.  A large Primary bedroom with ensuite and walk in closet also enjoys access to the second-floor screened patio. A two car garage for jet skis, kayaks and of course cars with easy access.  River Harbor West is a maintenance free community of 36 homes all set on the Manatee River.  A short stroll from the house and you can access the recently updated, private Clubhouse, screened patio, pickleball and tennis court and a large heated pool and spa.  Walk down the Trex dock to your boat slip and farther down to the picnic table to sit with friends overlooking the water.  The many additional amenities of NW Bradenton are only a few miles away.  These include Robinson Preserve, DeSoto Park and the beautiful beaches of Anna Maria Island.  With over 3400 sf under air, this home is waiting for a new owner to make it their own.
